    • getPriority

      int getPriority()
      Prioritization of kernel amongst different devices. By default we assume
priority is 0. The higher the priority the better. By default (i.e. if
this is not set), we prefer GPU kernels over CPU.
      int32 priority = 6;
      Returns:
      The priority.
